001package edu.cnm.deepdive.zoomattendance.model.dao;
002
003import androidx.lifecycle.LiveData;
004import androidx.room.Dao;
005import androidx.room.Delete;
006import androidx.room.Insert;
007import androidx.room.OnConflictStrategy;
008import androidx.room.Query;
009import androidx.room.Update;
010import edu.cnm.deepdive.zoomattendance.model.entity.ZoomMeeting;
011import io.reactivex.rxjava3.core.Maybe;
012import io.reactivex.rxjava3.core.Single;
013import java.util.Collection;
014import java.util.List;
015
016
017@SuppressWarnings("unused")
018@Dao
019public interface ZoomMeetingDao {
020
021  @Insert
022  Single<Long> insert(ZoomMeeting zoomMeeting);
023
024  @Insert(onConflict = OnConflictStrategy.IGNORE)
025  Single<List<Long>> insert(Collection<ZoomMeeting> zoomMeetings);
026
027  @Delete
028  Single<Integer> delete(ZoomMeeting zoomMeeting);
029
030  @Query("SELECT * FROM zoom_meeting WHERE zoom_meeting_id = :id")
031  LiveData<ZoomMeeting> select(long id);
032
033  @Query("SELECT * FROM zoom_meeting WHERE student_id = :studentId ORDER BY started DESC")
034  LiveData<List<ZoomMeeting>> selectByStudentId(long studentId);
035
036  @Query("SELECT * FROM zoom_meeting ORDER BY student_id, started")
037  LiveData<List<ZoomMeeting>> get();
038
039  @Query("SELECT * FROM zoom_meeting WHERE student_id = :studentId AND uuid = :uuid")
040  Maybe<ZoomMeeting> selectByStudentAndUUID(long studentId, String uuid);
041
042}
